findings.title: Inflation Attack Prevention Can Lead to Stuck Funds Minor
findings.description: The `StrategyBase` contract's defense against inflation attacks can lead to stuck funds due to enforcing a minimum total share amount.

findings.title: DelayedWithdrawalRouter – Anyone Can Claim Earlier Than Intended on Behalf of Someone Else
findings.description: The `DelayedWithdrawalRouter` has two functions to claim delayed withdrawals: one for the recipient to call themselves and one to claim on behalf of someone else, but the latter function is not permissioned and can be called at any time.
